ActCanada National Marine Conservation Areas Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the Canada National Marine Conservation Areas Act
PrecisOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the Canada National Marine Conservation Areas Act which complete the establishment process by adding the legal description of the Gwaii Haanas Marine Area to Schedule 2 to the Act. The Gwaii Haanas Marine Area now enjoys the highest standard of legal protection afforded by Canada.
